r happens **before any tokens are generated**, it:\n\n- Marks the account as exhausted until its reset (or a fallback cooldown)\n- Rotates to another account and retries\n\n## Checks\n\n```bash\nnpm run lint\nnpm run tsgo\nnpm run test\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776159362216}}
