l all-hands that selected pilot direction and clarified go-to-market priorities.\n  Tags: internal, meeting, neuratri, sales\n\n- notes/neuratri/meetings/internal/2026-01-29 client intake questionnaire design.md\n  Description: Internal design review for intake logic and structured discovery data quality.\n  Tags: forms, internal, meeting, neuratri\n\n- notes/neuratri/meetings/internal/2026-02-18 website services observability.md\n  Description: Internal meeting aligning website messaging with service packaging and monitoring strategy.\n  Tags: internal, meeting, neuratri, website\n\n- project/frigate-lxc/create-frigate-lxc-proxmox9-focus.md\n  Description: Decision note for create-frigate-lxc task to prioritize Proxmox 9 and use a dedicated LXC with Docker for Frigate, including validated host readiness and completed storage re-home.\n  Tags: frigate, proxmox, lxc, docker, project-decision, create-frigate-lxc, gpu, storage\n\n- project/frigate-lxc/projects/vm103/frigate-lxc-setup.md\n  Description: VM103 frigate LXC setup with organized files and clean commits\n  Tags: vm103, frigate, monitoring, commits, setup, home-lab\n\n- project/harness-utils/changelog.md\n  Description: Development history and notable repo structure changes for harness-utils\n  Tags: project, changelog, repo\n\n- project/home-assistant-da/external-runtime-timeout-ownership.md\n  Description: Defines timeout-clear ownership in home-assistant-da runtime instead of HA bridge automations.\n  Tags: home-assistant-da, presence, runtime, timeouts\n\n- project/home-assistant-da/global-luminance-contract.md\n  Description: Defines single-source luminance behavior for all areas in home-assistant-da.\n  Tags: home-assistant-da, luminance, runtime, sensors\n\n- project/home-assistant-da/migrate-ha-areas-decisions.md\n  Description: Canonical decision record for migrate-ha-areas runtime architecture and timeout mapping.\n  Tags: decisions, home-assistant-da, migrate-ha-areas, timeouts, vm103\n\n- project/